50|$|Since 2002, Seabees have {{provided}} critical and tactical construction skills {{in an effort}} to win {{the hearts and minds of}} locals in the Philippines. Their efforts have begun to deter the rising influence of radical terrorists in the southern Philippines, most notably the <b>Abu</b> <b>Sayyaf's</b> jungle training area. Seabees work along with Army, Marines, and Air Force under Joint Special Operations Task Force-Philippines.|$|R
